    <section class="workbench-page" data-workbench-page="repair" id="repair-center" hidden data-marker="Repair Center controlled flow no one-click full repo repair Start Safe Repair 安全修复入口"><div class="page-header"><div><p class="page-kicker" data-i18n="repair.kicker">安全修复</p><h2 data-i18n="repair.title">安全修复</h2><p data-i18n="repair.subtitle">所有修复必须经过意图预览 → 审批 → allowedFiles → 补丁方案 → rollback manifest → 自动审查 → go/no-go。</p></div><button type="button" class="btn primary" data-workbench-action="start-safe-repair" data-testid="start-safe-repair-button" data-i18n="repairStartSafeRepair">开始安全修复</button></div><div class="page-grid"><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="repair.what">这个页面是干什么的？</h3><p data-i18n="repair.whatText">当系统报错、验证失败或 UI 行为异常时，从这里进入安全修复流程。</p><p class="next-step" data-i18n="repair.next">下一步：点击“开始安全修复”，填写 allowedFiles，再预览意图。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="repair.safeRoute">安全修复流程</h3><p data-i18n="repair.safeRouteText">意图预览 → 人工审批 → allowedFiles → 补丁方案 → rollback manifest → 自动审查 → go/no-go。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="repair.blocked">为什么不能一键全仓修复？</h3><p data-i18n="repair.blockedText">为了防止误改、误删和误发布，系统不提供一键全仓修复、workspace cleanup、git reset、git clean 或发布操作。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="repair.failureTitle">修复失败怎么办？</h3><p data-i18n="repair.failureText">如果结果是不通过或需要人工复核，请查看阻止原因、evidence 和诊断中心，再重新限定 allowedFiles。</p><div class="toolbar"><button type="button" class="btn" data-workbench-nav="help" data-testid="repair-to-help" data-i18n="actions.openHelp">打开帮助</button><button type="button" class="btn" data-workbench-nav="diagnostics" data-testid="repair-to-diagnostics" data-i18n="actions.openDiagnostics">打开诊断</button></div></article></div></section>
    <section class="workbench-page" data-workbench-page="help" id="help-runbook" hidden data-marker="Help / Runbook Help Runbook visible useful system manual FAQ allowedFiles full-open safe repair"><div class="page-header"><div><p class="page-kicker" data-i18n="help.kicker">帮助</p><h2 data-i18n="help.title">系统说明书</h2><p data-i18n="help.subtitle">这不是工程提示，而是给用户看的完整 Runbook：系统是什么、每个模块怎么用、如何安全修复。</p></div></div><div class="page-grid"><details class="help-item" open data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.systemTitle">这个系统是什么</summary><p data-i18n="help.systemText">AI Gateway Workbench 是本地 AI 网关工作台，用来统一 Chat、知识库、模型、Local Agent、审批、修复和诊断。</p></details><details class="help-item" open data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.chatTitle">如何开始对话</summary><p data-i18n="help.chatText">打开 Chat，直接输入问题并发送。需要配置模型时点“配置模型”，需要改文件时不要绕过 Local Agent 审批。</p></details><details class="help-item" open data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.startTitle">新用户 3 步开始</summary><p data-i18n="help.startText">第一步去 Chat 提问；第二步需要查资料时用 Knowledge / RAG；第三步需要修改文件或修复系统时用 Local Agent / Repair Center。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.moduleTitle">每个模块用途</summary><p data-i18n="help.moduleText">Chat 用于对话；Search 用于找页面；Knowledge 用于 RAG；Models 用于模型和 Provider 配置；Local Agent 用于受控本地自动化；Approvals 用于审批和结果；Repair Center 用于安全修复；Settings 用于语言和启动；Diagnostics 用于历史 evidence。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.agentTitle">Local Agent 怎么用</summary><p data-i18n="help.agentText">先描述任务，再预览意图，填写 allowedFiles，生成补丁方案，人工批准，自动审查，最后看 go/no-go。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="helpModelConfig">如何配置模型</summary><p data-i18n="help.modelConfigText">进入模型配置页，查看当前 Provider、Base URL、Model ID 和 API Key 状态。Workbench 不显示 API key，不读取 .env，不自动调用 paid provider，也不改变默认 /chat 链路。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary>allowedFiles</summary><p data-i18n="help.allowedFilesText">allowedFiles 必须是 repo-relative path，例如 apps/ai-gateway-service/src/ui/consolePage.js。不要填全仓，也不要填 legacy/、.env、.git 或 node_modules。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary>Manual Approval Mode</summary><p data-i18n="help.manualText">Manual Approval Mode 要求用户看过风险、diffPreview 和 rollback manifest 后显式批准。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary>Auto Review Mode</summary><p data-i18n="help.autoReviewText">Auto Review Mode 只运行白名单命令，最多受控轮次，失败即停，不会无限修复。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.fullOpenTitle">为什么禁用 Full-open</summary><p data-i18n="help.fullOpenText">Full-open 会放大误改、误删和误发布风险，所以系统保持禁用。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.repairTitle">如何安全修复系统</summary><p data-i18n="help.repairText">从 Repair Center 点击“开始安全修复”，进入 Local Agent，先填写 allowedFiles，再预览意图；不能跳过审批。</p></details><details class="help-item" data-workbench-control="help-section"><summary data-i18n="help.faqTitle">常见问题</summary><p data-i18n="help.faqText">为什么不能一键全仓修复？因为必须先限定 allowedFiles。为什么按钮 disabled？因为当前 UI-only 阶段没有真实 handler 或缺少审批条件。为什么不能 commit/push/deploy？因为本地修复闭环只负责受控 patch 和审查。</p></details></div></section>
    <section class="workbench-page" data-workbench-page="settings" id="page-settings" hidden data-marker="Settings page visible model configuration launcher language safety defaults"><div class="page-header"><div><p class="page-kicker" data-i18n="settings.kicker">设置</p><h2 data-i18n="settings.title">设置</h2><p data-i18n="settings.subtitle">这里组织语言、模型配置入口、桌面启动和安全默认值；不新增 Provider、route 或执行能力。</p></div><button type="button" class="btn primary" data-workbench-action="configure-model" data-testid="settings-configure-model" data-i18n="actions.configureModel">配置模型</button></div><div class="page-grid"><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="settings.language">语言设置</h3><p data-i18n="settings.languageText">语言偏好写入 localStorage：aiGatewayWorkbenchLanguage，刷新后保留。</p><p class="next-step" data-i18n="settings.languageNext">下一步：使用顶部中文 / English 切换。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="settings.model">模型配置</h3><p data-i18n="settings.modelText">模型配置入口会带你进入 Models 页面，那里说明 Provider、API Key、Base URL 和 Model ID。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="settings.launcher">桌面启动</h3><p data-i18n="settings.launcherText">可以使用 Windows 启动脚本或桌面快捷方式打开 Workbench。</p></article><article class="page-card"><h3 data-i18n="settings.security">安全默认值</h3><p data-i18n="settings.securityText">Full-open disabled。不会 commit / push / deploy / release。不会读取 .env / secrets。</p></article></div></section>
