            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Dirty workspace refresh"><strong>dirty workspace 刷新</strong><div class="muted">未提交材料在验证通过前都视为临时状态。</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="workforce-guide" data-phase="phase248a-personal-knowledge-query-templates" data-operator-section="knowledge-query-templates">
