          <ul>
            <li data-marker="Each template includes question, expected sources, expected answer format, stale evidence caution, and what not to conclude.">每个模板都包含问题、预期来源、回答格式、旧 evidence 提醒和不能推出的结论。</li>
            <li data-marker="Use templates for current project status, current blocker, latest phase, sealed capability, preview-only capability, and next task.">用于询问当前项目状态、当前 blocker、最新 phase、已封板能力、preview-only 能力和下一条任务。</li>
            <li data-marker="Do not conclude production vector RAG, GraphRAG, real Codex exec, commercial readiness, or clean workspace without current evidence.">没有当前 evidence 时，不得推出生产级 vector RAG、GraphRAG、真实 Codex 执行、商业化 ready 或 clean workspace。</li>
