            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Docs citation"><strong>docs 引用</strong><div class="muted">优先引用 final/closure 文档；被替代的旧文档标为历史参考。</div></div>
            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Handoff citation caution"><strong>handoff 引用提醒</strong><div class="muted">Codex handoff/review 在 evidence 封板前只作工作循环上下文。</div></div>
            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Missing citation means uncertain"><strong>缺引用就是不确定</strong><div class="muted">缺少引用时要求重新验证，不要断言当前状态。</div></div>
