        </div>
        <div class="workforce-guide" data-phase="phase250a-personal-knowledge-freshness-guard" data-operator-section="knowledge-freshness-guard">
          <strong data-marker="Freshness Guard: Current fact order -> Latest evidence first -> Phase number caution -> Closure snapshot priority -> Dirty workspace warning -> Mark uncertain.">新鲜度防护：当前事实顺序 -> 最新 evidence 优先 -> phase 编号提醒 -> closure snapshot 优先 -> dirty workspace 警告 -> 标记不确定。</strong>
          <ul>
            <li data-marker="Use latest passed evidence, then closure snapshot, then final docs, README/AGENTS, older evidence, and historical legacy reference.">事实优先级：最新 passed evidence、closure snapshot、final docs、README/AGENTS、旧 evidence、legacy 历史参考。</li>
            <li data-marker="Document update time is not enough; check verifier status and phase order.">只看文档更新时间不够，必须看 verifier 状态和 phase 顺序。</li>
            <li data-marker="Mark uncertain when citation is missing, evidence failed, or dirty workspace overlaps the answer.">缺引用、evidence failed 或 dirty workspace 与答案重叠时，必须标记不确定。</li>
