        <div class="workforce-guide" data-phase="phase251a-personal-knowledge-ui-guide" data-operator-section="knowledge-ui-guide">
          <strong data-marker="Knowledge UI Guide: Enter knowledge area -> Source load/list -> RAG chat -> Citation/highlight -> Trust and stale answer check -> Convert to next task.">知识库 UI 指引：进入知识区 -> 来源加载/列表 -> RAG 聊天 -> 引用/高亮 -> 可信度和旧答案检查 -> 转成下一条任务。</strong>
          <div class="workforce-role-grid">
