            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Citation/highlight"><strong>引用/高亮</strong><div class="muted">只有引用指向当前文档或最新 passed evidence 时，才信任答案。</div></div>
            <div class="workforce-card" data-marker="Convert to next task"><strong>转成下一条任务</strong><div class="muted">把有引用的回答转成决策面板输入，或转成有边界的手动 handoff。</div></div>
