        <div class="workforce-guide" data-phase="phase254a-personal-knowledge-operator-manual" data-operator-section="knowledge-operator-manual">
          <strong data-marker="Knowledge Operator Manual: Daily knowledge use -> First source selection -> Citation and freshness -> Conflict handling -> Next Codex task -> Stop rules.">知识库操作手册：每日知识使用 -> 首批来源选择 -> 引用和新鲜度 -> 冲突处理 -> 下一条 Codex 任务 -> 停止规则。</strong>
